## Interfaces

Use the {{ connector_name | title }} connector through the Airbyte Agent CLI, the Python SDK, or the API.

### CLI

Install the CLI:

```bash
curl -fsSL https://airbyte.ai/install.sh | bash
```

Authenticate with Airbyte:

```bash
airbyte-agent login
```

Create the connector. The CLI opens the hosted setup flow:

```bash
{{ cli_connector_create(connector_name) }}
```

Describe the connector to see its supported entities and actions:

```bash
{{ cli_connector_describe(connector_name) }}
```
